ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAmendments to Annex I of the International Convention against Doping in Sport
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to ACCEPT, on behalf of the Government of Canada, that the AMENDMENTS TO ANNEX I OF THE INTERNATIONAL CONVENTION AGAINST DOPING IN SPORT, notified to the States Parties on October 1, 2019, be binding on Canada.
